<hr />

<div class="row col-xs-12" style="margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 5px; margin-top:30px;">
    <div class="row ">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
            <img src="~/Pictures/PRIHATIN02.png" class="img-thumbnail img-thumbnail" alt="PRIHATIN" />
            <p class="lead" align="justify" style="margin-top: 20px;">A web application to calculate how much a family or an individual can get the money from government based on the family qualification.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="col-md-6" style=" margin-top: 40px;">
        <h2>PRIHATIN Economic Stimulus Package</h2>
        <p class="lead" align="justify">
            The PRIHATIN Economic Stimulus Package (ESP) was unveiled by The Prime Minister on 27 March 2020.
            The PRIHATIN package will provide immediate assistance to ease the burden of people.
            This web helps people to calculate their ESP of how much they will receive based on the family qualification.
        </p>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6" style=" margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 80px;">
        <h2>Movement Control Order (MCO)</h2>
        <p class="lead" align="justify">
            The Movement Control Order has been announced by The Prime Minister on 16 March 2020. The initial period of
            the order is taking place starting from 18 March 2020 onwards until 31 March 2020. This page will showcase
            information on the order and will be updated from time to time. All of the information here are sourced from
            the Prime Minister’s Office, National Security Council, The Prime Minister’s Department and the National News Agency,
            BERNAMA. Latest updates can also be accessed from
            <a href="http://www.jpm.gov.my/ms/content/web-banner-covid-19" target="_blank">The Prime Minister’s Department website</a> and
            <a href="https://www.mkn.gov.my/web/ms/soalan-lazim-faq-mengenai-perintah-kawalan-pergerakan/" target="_blank">The National Security Council website</a>
        </p>

    </div>

</div>